  <body>
    <h1>Space Dodge with the Crowd!</h1>
    <p>Instructions: Dodge the incoming asteroids using the left and right arrow keys. 
       For every second your team plays, your bonus increases. Play to win a max bonus of $2.00!<br>
       The green box shows the aggregate position of other members in your team.<br>
       To change how the aggregate position is calculated, click the various buttons below.<br><br>
       <button id="median">Median</button> <button id="majority">Majority</button><br><br>
       <em><b>To begin playing, click the start button!</b></em>
       <button id="start">Start</button>
     </p>

    <p> There are currently <span id="numPlayers">no</span> players.</p> 
    
